Your Akismet API Key:<br /><br />The Akismet API Key is not required for your <a target="_blank" href="http://glowhost.com">GlowHost</a> Spam-O-Matic to function, but we suggest obtaining one. If you obtain a key and save it here, any spammers that are able to sneak by the automated checks and manage to post on your forum, can be automatically submitted to the Akismet database. <br /><br /> * In order to auto-submit to Akismet, "<b>Akismet: Auto-submit from Moderation Tools</b>" (below) needs to be set to Yes, assuming that you have an API Key.</i><br /><br />Akismet has free and licensed keys available depending on your situation. To obtain a key for your forum, visit <a target="_blank" href=" http://akismet.com/">Akismet.com</a> and choose the most appropriate option.